{"tid":1439328,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"致 鄭月娥女士","createTime":"2019-08-10T05:25:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T05:26:48.000Z","uid":263806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e6eeb29c76ba0b1579815ea5e28c98bce2c2acfc","tid":1439328,"uid":263806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:25:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">獨立調查委員會並非只針對警方<br />\n<br />\n是針對整場反送中運動去調查</span><br />\n<br />\n五大訴求中的其中一項：<br />\n成立獨立調查委員會，追究警隊濫權<br />\n<br />\n追究警隊濫權是抗爭者們最重視的方向<br />\n<br />\n但 獨立調查委員會<br />\n亦可就運動背後所謂有外國勢力的方向去調查<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請別再丟女人的臉<br />\n別再身體力行去侮辱「女強人」這個稱呼<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2kwvYJV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2kwvYJV.png&h=501077b3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"db57499d175555939e80da050d0dbb0bae4ac252","tid":1439328,"uid":263806,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:25:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0j9hAkN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0j9hAkN.png&h=47979cda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、成立獨立調查委員會，<br />\n        徹查反送中運動中所有不合理的事情，包捨：追究警隊濫權、官黑事件<br />\n五、立即實行雙真普選<br />\n六、要求永不落實「社會信用評分系統」<br />\n七、要求移除全港「多功能智慧燈柱」<br />\n<br />\n〈光復香港 時代革命〉"},{"pid":"2451070a2d12f7307bc5d32a268498a32f97fb8d","tid":1439328,"uid":263806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:26:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O5fs0Yn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO5fs0Yn.jpg&h=8b099365&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fcb77e2a0ab0bd0f208a10ed10035d8ed42e4eb7","tid":1439328,"uid":263806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:26:48.000Z","msg":"共產黨手法<br />\n<br />\n1970年，蘇聯KGB特工Yuri Bezmenov叛變（無中譯，Google譯做 尤里&middot;貝茲諾夫），投靠美國，並公開蘇聯情報部門顛覆敵對國家社會嘅方法。由意志敗壞（demoralisation）開始，令到整個社會感到無助，唔團結，冷感，撕